= SDL_GetDisplayMode =
Use this function to fill in information about a specific display mode.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetDisplayMode(int              index,
                       SDL_DisplayMode* mode)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''index'''
|the index of the display mode
|-
|'''mode'''
|points to the mode of the display
|}

